    "en": {
      "title": "The truth about the deceased Maskelia girl should be ascertained",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The body of a hillbilly girl, who allegedly fell into a swimming pool while going for housework, was buried today (22) at the public cemetery in Moka Gardens, Maskelia.",
        "A 16-year-old girl named Ramani of Mokka sub-division estate, Maskelia, was employed as a domestic worker six months ago.",
        "Worked at the home of a relative of Minister Prasanna Ranatunga in Gampaha.",
        "He died on the 19th after working there for about 6 months. It is said that he died due to suffocation after falling into the swimming pool.",
        "The deceased girl's father left her at an early age. The mother has also remarried. Due to this, the people of the town say that he grew up in the warmth of his uncle.",
        "People are demanding that the truth about the girl's death be ascertained."
      ],
